            { type = "p", text = "As we’ve accumulated a few days of data and player feedback following the 12.0.5 update, we’re planning to make adjustments that address outliers in both group play and in PvP. The following changes will go live with scheduled weekly maintenance in each region (on May 5 in this region)." },
